REQ: 实现可拖拽的青色方块，拖拽时变色，松手后回到初始位置
API: Graphics.fillStyle, Graphics.fillRect, Graphics.generateTexture, setInteractive, on('drag'), on('dragstart'), on('dragend')
STEPS:
